title: Driving Turner Motorsports' BMW Z4 GTD - /MATT FARAH
description:
How much faster is a race car than a street car? To find out, Matt drove BMW's  newest version of the Z4, the Z4 sdrive35i, and then jumped into a championship winning Z4 that was built by Turner Motorsport. 

The difference, and abilities, are staggering.
tags: BMW Z4, GTD, Turner Motorsport, Le Mans, motorsport, Z4
